HEADWORD: Cosmographer
<hw>Cos*mog"ra*pher</hw> <pr>(-r?-f?r)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who
describes the world or universe, including the heavens and the
earth.</def><-- =cosmologist -->⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

